headline: Anheuser-Busch Stock Surges 6% This Week on Earnings Beat and Analyst Upgrades
summary: Anheuser-Busch InBev (NYSE:BUD) delivered a 6% gain this week, outpacing both the S&P 500 and its consumer staples peers. The world’s largest brewer is trading at $80.39, approaching its 52-week high of $81.56. Three distinct storylines drove the move, each revealing where this company stands heading into 2026.
